### **4. 23_RealTimeGraphStream**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes incoming numeric data as a real-time, scrollable graph with smooth updates.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealTimeGraphStream - Live Metric Stream Visualizer

RealTimeGraphStream transforms numerical input from scripts, sensors, or APIs into smooth, animated graphs.

## Features
- Scrollable line chart  
- Adjustable speed  
- Lightweight interface  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/23_RealTimeGraphStream.git
cd 23_RealTimeGraphStream
python visualize.py
